'''天主教卡希托教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Caxitonensis}}；{{lang-pt|Diocese de Caxito}}）是[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教羅安達總教區|羅安達總教區]]。

教區於2007年6月6日成立<ref>{{cite web |title=CAXITONENSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/benedict-xvi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_ben-xvi_apc_20070606_caxitonensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-06-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616142302/https://w2.vatican.va/content/benedict-xvi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_ben-xvi_apc_20070606_caxitonensis.html |archivedate=2020-06-16 |language=la |date=2007-06-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，位於首都[[羅安達|羅安達]]北郊，2010年時有240,000名教友（佔轄區總人口42.6%）、10個[[堂區|堂區]]和25名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-en|瑪利斯·卡穆托|Maurício Camuto|瑪利斯·奧斯定·卡穆托}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 15.06.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/15/200615b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615120343/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/15/200615b.html |archivedate=2020-06-15 |language=en |date=2020-06-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

